title: Bar Rescue Complete Season 3
description: This is the complete season 3. Unlike the others on here, I took the liberty of adding the rest into one complete torrent. Files are a mix between AVI and MKV mostly. I took the time and checked every episode's air date and put them in order. Also included are the Lost Episode and Hurricane Sandy Bar Rescue episode. I did not add the Top 10 episodes though, didn't feel the need to watch them. I hope this comes in handy instead of painstakingly searching each episode, like I did. Enjoy the show and don't forget to seed!
